+------------------------------+
| Basic Information:           |
+------------------------------+
| This map was designed for
| demolition team play on
| Counter-Strike: Source.  It
| is ideal for small LANs and
| CPU opponents.
| 
+------------------------------+
| Map specifics:
+------------------------------+
| Players:  4-12 (Ideal)
| Spawn Points:  24 Total
|    T: 12 (Two Groups of 6)
|    CT: 12 (Two Groups of 6)
| Advantage:  None.  Map is
|             completely
|             symmetrical
|
+------------------------------+
| Installation:
+------------------------------+
| Place "de_kyle.bsp" and
| "de_kyle.NAV" in
| your Counter-Strike: Source
| map folder
| 
| C:\
|  Program Files\
|   Steam\
|    SteamApps\
|     [Your Steam Username]\ 
|      counter-strike source\
|       cstrike\
|        maps\
|
+------------------------------+
| Known Bugs:
+------------------------------+
| When the map is run with
| bots for the first time,
| a .NAV file will be created
| that allows the bots to jump
| off the level to their death.
| This is a known issue.
| This release is reccommended
| for human play.
| Included is the .NAV file
| that was created at the time
| of the completion of the map.
|
+------------------------------+
| Credit / Etc.:
+------------------------------+
| This map may be distributed
| and played freely, as long
| as this documentation is
| included with it.
| 
| Any questions or comments
| can be sent to:
| 
| Oblyter8ed@gmail.com
| 
| Enjoy!
|
+------------------------------+
